Package org.assistments.connector.service

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AccountService
    This interface contains the operations on ASSISTments user account and manages the association between ASSISTments user and Partner user.
    AssignmentService
    This interface contains operations on ASSISTments assignment and manages the associations between ASSISTments assignment and Partner assignment.
    ProblemSetService
    This interface contain the operations on the problem set
    SchoolService
    This interface contains the operations on ASSISTments School
    ShareLinkService
    This interface contains the operations on share link and manages the association between Partner user and share link
    StudentClassService
    This interface contains operations on ASSISTments student class and manages the associations between ASSISTments student class and Partner student class.
    UserService Deprecated
